    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ragdoll Rumble is a chaotic party game where toy wizards unleash wild spells in explosive spellcasting battles. Cast crazy abilities, outsmart your opponents, and prove to your friends that you are the dominant doll!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast Spells, Cause Havoc!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/4e6ac42aa6fca7f20a4c28d870a447aa.poster.avif?t=1757122648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/4e6ac42aa6fca7f20a4c28d870a447aa.webm?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/4e6ac42aa6fca7f20a4c28d870a447aa.mp4?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield an arsenal of zany spells to dash around, launch into the air, or blast your friends off the map. Search for Elixirs to unlock even more insane abilities—like fireballs, swirling whirlpools, or lightning storms that make the battlefield dangerous and unpredictable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local &amp; Remote Splitscreen Mayhem!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/d702fba3adedf51023aeb0a827512d49.poster.avif?t=1757122648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/d702fba3adedf51023aeb0a827512d49.webm?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/d702fba3adedf51023aeb0a827512d49.mp4?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against or alongside your friends in 2-4 player local splitscreen, or connect via Steam Remote Play to bring the chaos online. With a variety of maps and game modes, every match is fresh, unpredictable, and full of surprises—like teleporters and boulder traps that shift the flow of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prove Yourself as the Dominant Doll!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/816bd8b1a15a8c3d29cfdd4d6241aacd.poster.avif?t=1757122648\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/816bd8b1a15a8c3d29cfdd4d6241aacd.webm?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059230/extras/816bd8b1a15a8c3d29cfdd4d6241aacd.mp4?t=1757122648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you team up or fight Free-For-All, cast Elixirs or rely on your fast mobile spells, compete with your friends to see who is blasted away in the chaos, and who reigns supreme in  the Ragdoll Rumble!</p>",
